description: Demolition of existing residential blocks and erection of four new residential blocks (part 3, part4, part 5 and part 6 storeys) to provide 185 residential units, comprising 69 x 1 bed, 57 x 2 bed, 55 x 3 bed  and 4 x 4 bed units, a community room and a children's play area, together with the provision of 57 car parking spaces and 39 bicycle spaces.
